---
title: Basa Masala with Basmati Rice and Peas
description: Masala curries are versatile tomato-based dishes that work with a variety of proteins and vegetables. Here, we're using basa, a white fish perfect for soaking up the delicious flavour of the masala curry sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R06_W35_UK_L23145-7_Main_low-1f5bdabf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/667adbab37bff126fa758b89-en-GB.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
author: Lily Stevens
cuisine: Indian
nutrition:
  calories: 636 kcal
  fat: 10 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
  carbohydrates: 85.6 g
  sugar: 14.5 g
